Title: Hunk Travellerr
DateModified: '2019-03-04'
DatePublished: '2019-03-04'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/hunk-travellerr
SetInCountry: India
Category: I didn't expect to find
AuthorName: Abhishek Kumar
AuthorCountry: India
Text: Once i and some of my friends are stuck in Island (Daman and Diu) which is situated
  near Gujarat.It was around 11 o'clock we didn't find any taxi or tempoo there we
  have to go atleast 40 km far at bus stand we are searching here and there then one
  police officer came and scolding us and asking very brutal questions one of my friend
  get anger then he said i will put all of you on lock up and beat very hard we all
  afraid and try to  convince some of my south Indian friends they talk in very peaceful
  way sir we are very sorry please let us go we are students we are searching to reach
  our home .We show our id card and everyone said sorry then he warn us and said get
  out from here by walking foot .Then after that one tempoo wala came the police officer
  said tempoo wala you can not give them lift and he ran away .Then tempoo wala also
  not allowed to shit there then we decided to go by walking then after some time
  one icecream delivery tempoo is going everyone try to stop please help please Stop
  the tempo then that person stop and we all shit on the roof of tempoo and take a
  long deep air after that we reach safely our destination and we give some money
  to ice cream wala .After we reach we laugh too much and enjoying the meal at restaurant.
